[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "结束了今天的任务之后，我和琴诺马不停蹄赶往医疗室。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "由脑部神经检查仪器改造而来的<orange>锚定装置</>就放置在这里，如今我已经十分熟悉使用方法。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在琴诺的帮助下，我将磁极贴片一一贴到头部的各个位置，随后在充满氟化碳的医疗舱中躺下，一旁的显示屏上开始出现代表大脑活动状态的波形图。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了避免意外情况——例如在记忆中受到严重冲击而被困于记忆中，一旦波形图上出现异常，琴诺就会立刻关闭锚定装置，而我会在大约5秒后回到现实。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我准备好了，开始吧。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "琴诺悖谬",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，请，请把手给我。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "琴诺的手抓住了我伸出的左手。为了在找到莫尔索后将她送回琴诺那里，这是必要的肢体接触。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着装置启动的蜂鸣声，我眼前的一切逐渐模糊消散。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次去第一次见到琴诺的地方看看吧，我在心里这样默念着，同时尽力构想出当天的画面。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "满是灰尘的公司安全屋，卡罗琳，茉莉安，琴诺……记忆中的一切逐渐变得清晰，黑暗中慢慢亮起了白炽灯的光芒——"
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对了，你见过这边的队员了吗？"
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出现了，我可靠的情报官小姐。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接下来我会说“还没有”，然后卡罗琳就会给我介绍茉莉安和琴诺。而如果不这样回答的话……"
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": ""
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "其实我见过了。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "静止卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "连同我在内，周围的一切骤然停止，像是被按下了暂停键。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "果然还是不行。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在第一次使用锚定装置时我就发现，记忆就是记忆，我并不能在“已经发生的”记忆中做出改变。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就像已经排列好的多米诺骨牌，抽走任何一块都无法继续下去。"
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": ""
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没有。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我已经通知她们了，应该也快到了。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随着我的“正确回答”，卡罗琳恢复了正常。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "噔~噔噔~噔~噔！"
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这位是茉莉安，你们应该挺熟了。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "又见面了，分析员，您路途上没遇到什么危险吧？"
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-3",
        "Flag": "b-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": ""
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "b-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "都很顺利。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有了前车之鉴，我并不打算再让记忆卡住。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我也和您有相同的感受。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这边是琴诺……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我随着卡罗琳的目光看去，所见的却是一头显眼的白发。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与记忆中初次见面无比怯懦的琴诺不同，站在卡罗琳身后的是一脸茫然的莫尔索。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与上一次的梦境相似，这次莫尔索直接代替了琴诺出现吗？"
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-4",
        "Flag": "b-4",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": ""
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "b-4-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "尝试接触莫尔索"
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我试着向莫尔索伸出手，可这个念头刚一出现，记忆立刻又定格下来，来自于“规则”的桎梏便是如此难以突破。"
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-5",
        "Flag": "b-5",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": ""
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "b-5-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "和莫尔索打招呼"
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果按照原本的记忆进行下去，也许还有转机。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我正准备开口，面前的莫尔索却忽然流出了眼泪。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "紧接着，她艰难地迈着步子，向我走来。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "莫尔索",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为什么——"
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "莫尔索",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看不到我呢——"
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "莫尔索",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "梦中的一切再次重演，她丢了魂般地扑到我的身上，泣不成声。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的身体轻盈而温暖，湿热的呼吸无比真实地充斥着我的胸口。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可是，为什么？"
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我显然已经接触到了莫尔索，可锚定装置并没有任何反应。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "换而言之，出现在我面前的并不是真正的莫尔索。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是记忆的世界，唯一的解释是，我现在看到的“莫尔索”是莫尔索的意识在这里留下的痕迹，她在那时拥抱的则是在我的记忆中一无所知的“我自己”。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚好错位了吗……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "事情愈发复杂起来了。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我被琴诺从医疗舱中扶起，额头上已经满是因为压力而渗出的汗珠。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "锚定装置只是辅助，构建过去的记忆还是需要靠我的大脑来完成，也因此每次使用都会带来不小的负荷。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "琴诺悖谬",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你的脸色不太好……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "琴诺悖谬",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我记得瑟瑞斯说这种时候需要停止使用锚定装置，休息三到五天……"
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没事的，琴诺。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我勉强挤出一个微笑——大概谁都骗不过的微笑。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我去找一下芙提雅她们吧。"
    }
]